            "id": 5933678,
            "title": "《大手成交》港交所一手約10萬股非自動對盤,涉資3295萬元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社10日專訊》港交所(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00388:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00388\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00388-HK</a>)於10:18am錄得1手10.46萬股非自動對盤,每股造315元,較上日收市價高4.4%,涉資3295萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　港交所現價升4.9%,報316.4元;成交667.99萬股,成交金額21.01億元,主動買沽比率56:44,資金淨主動買入2.17億元。(rw)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
